\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
We designed different EEG signal processing pipelines that each create a
 specific visualization tailored to identify specific elements in the signal.
 The details of these pipelines are transparent to the user.
 Each pipeline corresponds to a mini-Teegi filter.
 In particular, we set up the following EEG signal processing pipelines:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
