 After the session, the experimenter had an informal talk with the participant.
 He corrected the answers, making sure the participant was not leaving with
 false knowledge, and explained in more detail some aspects of the system
 (e.g.
 relationship between visual filter and attentional states, the various
 effects of meditation, ...).
 This phase lasted from 30 min to 1 hour depending on the participant's
 curiosity.
