\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "Vosniadou1992"

\end_inset

.
 This is particularly true for brain activity that is difficult to understand
 because it cannot be sensed 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "Damasio1994"

\end_inset

, contrary to other activities (e.g.
 respiratory) that are perceived through sensory-motor mechanisms.
 Hence, brain activities need to be conceptualized, and the success of learning
